title: Evan Patterson from Jaye Jayle, Young Widows & Breather Resist
itunes:title: Evan Patterson from Jaye Jayle, Young Widows & Breather Resist
description:
I am honored to have Evan Patterson from Jaye Jayle, Young Widows, Breather Resist and so much more on the show today. Him and I go way back but it's been years since we spoke and dove right into it discussing his musical identity, living in Louisville and DIY living at all costs. He's an inspiring musician that continues to push himself with all of his work.
